{"tid":2300194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一下爆頭！恐怖影片! 綠燈起步 二段式左轉單車橫越砂石車頭前慘遭輾斃","createTime":"2020-11-25T10:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T10:56:34.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6397741c4e74adfb20db68e0d0f956b4e5452eba","tid":2300194,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A94beSN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA94beSN.jpg&h=99cc5e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M52Z1Fu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM52Z1Fu.jpg&h=da18175a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nWTsrCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnWTsrCo.jpg&h=ed6d89f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XPCEZvl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXPCEZvl.jpg&h=cdf6c4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/R4y85iW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FR4y85iW.jpg&h=9111f261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南投縣草屯鎮草溪路昨（24日）下午3時許發生一起死亡車禍，一名騎單車的男子，原本與<br />\n一輛砂石車併排停等紅燈，但綠燈起步時單車男不知何故，突然左轉橫越砂石車頭前，結<br />\n果遭撞倒連人帶車捲入車底，並在前輪輾壓，送醫不治。旁邊目擊過程的店家女員工嚇得<br />\n用手掩面逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36362cA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36362cA&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuws4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=cf48c998\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36362cA</a>"},{"pid":"76d39b27ece6f7176a98ee809636dd1d094267a2","tid":2300194,"uid":188310,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:14:43.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚弱智重新投胎咪好囉"},{"pid":"c57c46429725da4